			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In this episode of the Ecommerce Podcast, host Shaun Ryan, CEO of <a href="http://www.sli-systems.com">SLI Systems</a>, interviews Laura Santos, Marketing Manager of <a href="http://www.envelopes.com">Envelopes.com</a>, a leading supplier of plain and printed envelopes to businesses, organizations, and individuals.</p>
<p>Laura explains how Envelopes.com is attracting customers to their site through paid search, text ads and display ads as well as putting some focus on remarketing for abandonment. Laura also discusses an upcoming feature to Envelopes.com that will allow their customers to personalize and design the products they are purchasing.</p>
<p>Tune in to find out more!</p>
<p>Length: 22 mins 36 secs</p>
