			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In this episode of the Ecommerce Podcast, host Shaun Ryan, CEO of <a href="http://www.sli-systems.com">SLI Systems</a>, interviews Justus Wilde, Online Strategy Director of <a href="http://www.amblique.com">Amblique</a>, a digital agency providing ecommerce solutions, content management systems, search engine optimization, and search engine marketing.</p>
<p>Justus discusses the difficulties retailers are having measuring attribution for their in-store and online purchases when channels are blurring together. He also touches on mobile shopping and how retailers should be aware of what devices their customers are using, whether phone or tablet, and optimize the retail site to suite the customers&#8217; behavior.</p>
<p>Tune in to find out more!</p>
<p>Length: 22 mins 9 secs</p>
