			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In this episode of the Ecommerce Podcast, host Shaun Ryan, CEO of <a href="http://www.sli-systems.com">SLI Systems</a>, interviews Chris Reighley, Director of Ecommerce at <a href="http://www.totes-isotoner.com/">Totes/Isotoner</a> a manufacturer and seller of rain and cold weather products.</p>
<p>Chris discusses how having an online presence has helped them to better connect with their customers and to gain valuable feedback to improve their business. Over the past 2 years, their ecommerce site has grown tremendously from less than half a percent to just over 2% of their wholesale business. As they look to continuously grow in 2012, Chris shares some of the things Totes/ISOTONER will be doing online including 3 big trends: selling internationally, mobile, and user generated content. </p>
<p>Tune in to find out more!</p>
<p>Length: 25 mins 23 secs</p>
