			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In this episode of the Ecommerce Podcast host Shaun Ryan, CEO of <a href="http://www.sli-systems.com">SLI Systems</a>, interviews George Eberstadt, CEO and Founder of <a href="http://www.turntonetworks.com/">TurnTo Networks</a>, a provider of Social Commerce applications for online merchants.</p>
